'''Green Emberü''' was the first planet that [[Michael George Ramer]] had visited with his mind.

== History ==
When Michael George Ramer landed on the most likely green planet, he described to the other members of the [[Notion Club]] that the world had organic life that was wholesome and longeval and rich.

== Other versions of the legendarium ==
In earlier drafts, Green Emberü was originally named as '''Gyönyörü'''.<ref>{{SD|2c}}, note 28</ref>
